@node "Disclaimer" "Disclaimer"

                                @{fg shine}Disclaimer
                                ~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

 Whilst writing this package, all of the scripts have undergone a great
 deal of testing. At the end of the day MailCheck works for me, however
 your mileage may vary! Since writing v1.3 I have used MailCheck over 2500
 times!

 I will not take responsibility in any way if MailCheck or any of the
 associated scripts fail and subsequently leave your modem on-line, trash
 your hard drive or blow up your monitor!
  

                    USE THESE SCRIPTS AT YOUR OWN RISK!

@endnode

@node "Copyright" "Copyright"

                                @{fg shine}Copyright
                                ~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

 MailCheck is released as Freeware.

 You may distribute it though out the Amiga community as long as the
 following conditions are maintained:

  * You do not try to take credit for my work. 

  * You do not sell it for profit. 

  * Before including it on a compilation disk or CD you must ask me first.

  * All the files must be distributed in single archive, compressed with
    either LHA or LZX.
  
