@node "Requirements" "Requirements"

                              @{fg shine}Requirements
                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

 YAM 2.0p4         -     Amiga mailer by Marcel Beck.
 Miami             -     TCP/IP stack by Holger Kruse.
 RexxMast          -     ARexx server by William S.Hawes. 

 CheckModem        -     Modem status tester by Nils Görs.
 Play16            -     Sample player by Thomas Wenzel.
 OkayDokey         -     Requester auto closer by Paul Huxham.
 RexxTricks        -     ARexx function library by Jürgen Kohrmeyer.
 Reqtools          -     Requester library by Nico Francois.
 RexxReqtools      -     ARexx function library by Rafael D'Halleweyn. 
 MUIRexx3.0        -     ARexx --> MUI interface by Russell Leighton.
 InputStream       -     ARexx server to "feed" input to the input stream
                         by Robert Hardy.

 All the programs required are available on the Aminet.  InputStream is
 included in the "extras" directory in this archive.

 In addition to this a fair number of AmigaDOS commands are also used by 
 MailCheck. These include: Status, CPU, Version, Break, Eval, Delete  and
 more.... Compatibility is not guaranteed with any "replacement" commands! 

 I would assume that you are already using Miami and YAM - if not then why
 did you download MailCheck? Maybe now would be a good time to change your
 TCP/IP stack and mail client?

 To make things as painless as possible, I have added NetLinks 
 support to this guide. Just click on the buttons below to download 
 the archives required from the Aminet mirror at uni-paderborn. 


    @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*CheckModem.lha*pub/aminet/comm/misc/*anon*anon"} <-- CheckModem    @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*Play16.lha*pub/aminet/mus/play/*anon*anon"} <-- Play16      @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*OkayDokey14.lha*pub/aminet/util/cdity/*anon*anon"} <-- OkayDokey


    @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*RexxTricks_386.lha*pub/aminet/util/rexx/*anon*anon"} <-- RexxTricks    @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*ReqtoolsUsr.lha*pub/aminet/util/libs/*anon*anon"} <-- Reqtools    @{"  " system "run >nil: sys:rexxc/rx NetLinks FTP ftp.uni-paderborn.de*RexxReqTools.lha*pub/aminet/util/rexx/*anon*anon"} <-- RexxReqtools


